reviewText: These SNL collections are by far the best of SNL for sure! The original crew in all their hilariously funny glory ;)

Bought this as a gift for my husband for Christmas as he's a huge SNL fan.  We watched a few episodes, and what great memories, but had some boring scenes as well.  Will have to see as we are able to watch more.  Gotta love the old episodes though from the 70's-beats what's on SNL today!
